				<h1>Reporting a New Bug</h1>
			</center>
			
		</font>
		
		
		<font size = 5 face="Arial"> 
		
			<br>
			<li>Click <a href="http://130.49.222.93/bugzilla/enter_bug.cgi" target="blank">here</a> to enter a new bug report
			<br>
			<br>
			<hr>
			<br>
			When reporting a bug you will be asked for some information:
			<br>
			<br>
			<li>Product - the product the bug occurred in
			<li>Version - the product version number
			<li>Component - which component was the bug in
			<li>General Computer Information - Platform, OS, etc
			<li>Priority and Severity - just how important is this bug
			<li>Assign To and CC - who will get this bug report
			<li>Summary and Description - be VERY specific
			<br>
			<br>
			<hr>
			<br>
			Bug reporting tips:
			<br>
			<br>
			<li>Give as much information as possible
			<li>Explain how to reproduce the bug
			<li>The more information that is provided, the easier (and more likely) the bug is to fix

